The watermarking approach used in this software is a keyed,
frequency-domain image-watermarking scheme. The algorithmic foundations
predate this implementation by decades; see in particular Cox, Kilian,
Leighton, and Shamoon, "Secure Spread Spectrum Watermarking for
Multimedia," IEEE Transactions on Image Processing, vol. 6, no. 12,
December 1997. This implementation is an independent, clean-room
realization and is not derived from, affiliated with, or compatible with
any third-party watermarking system.
